\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 The matrix of button shows the choices of clefs.  The are arranged so that clefs of keycentre C are given in the first row; keycentre F in the second row; keycentre G in the third row; percussion in the fourth.  For each row, one or more different designs of clef are provided.\par
\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0\fs24\f1\b0\i0 L\f1 ine\f0\f0 :\f0   Specifies the line of the staff associated with the key center.\f0 \par
